# Threat Modeling Process Diagram

direction: right

assets: Assets to Protect {
  data: Sensitive Data
  systems: Critical Systems
  users: User Accounts
}

threats: Threat Sources {
  external: External Attackers
  internal: Insider Threats
  accidental: Accidental Exposure
}

vulnerabilities: Vulnerabilities {
  software: Software Flaws
  config: Misconfigurations
  process: Weak Processes
}

controls: Security Controls {
  preventive: Preventive Controls
  detective: Detective Controls
  corrective: Corrective Controls
}

assets --> vulnerabilities: Exposes
threats --> vulnerabilities: Exploits
vulnerabilities --> controls: Mitigated By
controls --> assets: Protects
